name: Nova Cannabis Inc.
longDescription: Nova Cannabis Inc is engaged in the operation of retail cannabis stores in Canada. It operates approximately 57 retail cannabis stores in Alberta, 16 in Ontario, and one in Saskatchewan. Some of its brands are Value Buds and Sweet Tree Cannabis Co. The company's products include Dried flowers, Pre-rolls, Candy and Cartridges, among others.
